title: Community Mixtape Vol. 2 | Blakinola

embed.description: Blakinola shouts out five YouTube creators you should check out. Have your own favorite creator? Give them a shout out in the comments.

body:
You might know Blakinola from TL;DR Patch Notes, champion previews, and more; now he's here to spread the YouTube love. Here's five content creators that Blakinola thinks you should be subscribed to!

Oh baby!

Which creator should make a mixtape next?
